alright. im going to be REAL mature like others and dedicate my entry to some people.
TO ALL THE HATERS THE FAKERS & THE WANNA-BES:

first of all- GET OVER YOURSELF. you need to grow up, and start worrying about your own problems instead of pointing out all of mine. no one said i was perfect, and i sure as hell dont even wanna try to be. to the ones that are upset that i dont ever hangout with you anymore- did you ever once think that maybe there was a reason for that? maybe i dont wanna hangout with you anymore. maybe i dont think i wanna even be around you, or your negative attitudes. im not going to show ANYONE sympathy for anything. we're all freaking grown-ass adults (almost) and we need to start acting like it. sure ill miss you when you move away jonathan, but im not gonna boo-hoo and act all depressed and call you every 10 minutes of my life to see if you wanna do something. ive always said THE PHONE WORKS BOTH WAYS. and if you arent ganna make the effort to dial my number and just ask me, then you sure as hell shouldnt expect me to. 
i dont appreciate you writing immature LJ entries about me, trying to bash me and make me look like a bad person- WITHOUT EVEN SAYING MY NAME. that just shows how immature you are. i dont get my feelings hurt easily, so if you ever wanna do that again- just go ahead and say my name. it'll be easier for everyone.
im sure you're pretty pissed off, but i honestly dont care. i know that what im saying is 100 percent right, and i really dont care if you agree with me or not. i know who all of my REAL friends are, and i know they have my back all the way.

TO ALL THE FAKERS ON MYSPACE AND LIVEJOURNAL STEALING MY PICTURES AND USING THEM AS THERES:

all you're telling these people is that you are insecure, ignorant, and last but not least: freakin IMMATURE. im not trying to act better than anyone else, but my GOD stop acting so immature all of the time.

BOTTOM LINE:
Embrace what you are and not just what you are- but who you are. Love your imperfections, they make you beautiful. Be beautiful from the inside out, its not all about physical appearance! And its more than what meets the eye. Stop hiding behind a photograph of your ideal self, and start becoming who you want to be. People will love you for who you are, if you're real. Being fake accomplishes nothing because you will always be the 2nd rate version, the immitation, never the duplication or the equal. Stop living a lie, it will only destroy your sense of self further. You only have one life to live so make the best of it...you wouldnt want to look back and realize you wasted your time trying to be someone else.
THANK YOU

wednesday- went back to the school to teach, and by the time scott picked me up around 3:15- i was so tired, i fell asleep in his car. then we went to marks house, and i slept on the couch while they watched the longest yard. woke up around 6, and went to church. the sermon was REALLY good. its weird when you dont wanna go to church- and you go anyway, and you end up being REALLY happy that you did, because it was something you needed to hear :)

i slept ALOT, and was lazy all day long. it felt good to relax. my feet hurt REALLY bad from standing up 7 hours everyday.

tomorrow i go back to HTMS to teach, scotts picking me up, and we're going to his house so i can help him study for some tests he has next week. and hopefully if we get done studying in time, we'll go see SAW 2.

I LOVE MY FRIENDS!

 

  • im not one of those girls that starves herself, or lives off of lettuce and rice cakes.
  • im a strong believer in keeping your friends close, and your enemies closer.
  • i dont like people that make fun of other people
  • my brother (andrew) is my hero. hands down.
  • i love jesus.
  • im a terrible driver. i ran into Chick-fil-A
  • im VERY tickelish
  • jealous people make me gag- but oh well.. we all have our moments.
  • i love to have fun
  • i love to make people laugh
  • i always smile. even if im having a crappy day.
  • i dont like blunt people- eventhough my best friend is the definition of BLUNT
  • i dont trust many people
  • i always apologize. even if its not my fault.
  • i like to take something HORRIBLE that happened to me, and make something good out of it. i have no regrets about anything.
  • i dislike copy-cats, or robots. BE A LEADER! NOT A FOLLOWER!
  • pastor david webb is the best youth pastor in the whole entire world. and everyone knows it.
  • amby franks is by far the most REAL, natural, and gorgeous girl i know. i think she should be the example of how girls should grow up to be.
  • ive been blessed with the greatest friends i could ever have. i wouldnt trade them for money or fame.
  • life is too good to be spending your time getting drunk or high, fighting over stupid things, holding grudges, never taking chances, or having regrets.

I don't need you to be in love with me

I need you to look at me in that way that shows me you truly care

I don't need a diamond ring

I need a hug

I don't need you to call me every hour

I need you to call me in the middle of the night because you can't sleep

I don't need you to take me to a fancy restaurant

I need you to bring over a pint of Ben and Jerry's ice cream and watch a movie with me


I don't need you to knock on my door to bring me flowers

I need you to throw a rock at my window in the middle of the night to tell me you missed me

I don't need you to write me poems about how you long to kiss my lips

I need you to kiss me because actions speak louder then words

I don't need you to be silent

I need you to scream out what you wanna say because sometimes I don't listen the first time

I don't need you to tell me I'm difficult

I need you to understand that I'm already aware

I don't need you to leave me alone when I'm mad so I can cool off

I need you to call me nonstop until I tell you what's wrong

I don't need you to agree with me

I need you to argue with me sometimes

I don't need you to let me do whatever I want

I need you to be the one to tell me when I'm doing something wrong

And when I don't listen, and I probably won't listen

I need you to take care of me

I don't need you to try to be perfect

I need you to bother me

I don't need you to always look fresh

I need you to be able to come to my house in basketball shorts and a tee

I don't need you to play it cool

I need you to act stupid and make me laugh

I don't need you to serenade me with love songs

I need you to sing the theme song to Blue's Clues with me

I don't need you to promise you'll never hurt me because I know at some point or another you will

I need you to hurt me and do everything you can to fix it

I don't need you to pay attention to me every second because I know you won't
